{
  "number": 69,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الحَاقَّةِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Haaqqa",
  "englishNameTranslation": "The Reality",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 5324,
      "text": "OH, THE LAYING-BARE of the truth!",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5325,
      "text": "How awesome that laying-bare of the truth!",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5326,
      "text": "And what could make thee conceive what that laying-bare of the truth will be?",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5327,
      "text": "THE LIE gave [the tribes of] Thamud and ‘Ad to [all tidings of] that sudden calamity!",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5328,
      "text": "Now as for the Thamud - they were destroyed by a violent upheaval [of the earth];",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5329,
      "text": "and as for the ‘Ad - they were destroyed by a storm wind furiously raging,",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5330,
      "text": "which He willed against them for seven nights and eight days without cease, so that in the end thou couldst see those people laid low [in death], as though they were so many [uprooted] trunks of hollow palm trees:",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5331,
      "text": "and dost thou now see any remnant of them?",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 566,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5332,
      "text": "And there was Pharaoh, too, and [many of] those who lived before him, and the cities that were overthrown - [all of them] indulged in sin upon sin",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5333,
      "text": "and rebelled against their Sustainer's apostles: and so He took them to task with a punishing grasp exceedingly severe!",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5334,
      "text": "[And] behold: when the waters [of Noah's flood] burst beyond all limits, it was We who caused you to be borne [to safety] in that floating ark,",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5335,
      "text": "so that We might make all this a [lasting] reminder to you all, and that every wide-awake ear might consciously take it in.",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5336,
      "text": "Hence, [bethink yourselves of the Last Hour,] when the trumpet [of judgment] shall be sounded with a single blast,",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5337,
      "text": "and the earth and the mountains shall be lifted up and crushed with a single stroke!",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5338,
      "text": "And so, that which must come to pass will on that day have come to pass;",
      "numberInSurah": 15,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5339,
      "text": "and the sky will be rent asunder - for, frail will it have become on that Day -;",
      "numberInSurah": 16,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5340,
      "text": "and the angels [will appear] at its ends, and, above them, eight will bear aloft on that Day the throne of thy Sustainer’s almightiness…",
      "numberInSurah": 17,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5341,
      "text": "On that Day you shall be brought to judgment: not [even] the most hidden of your deeds will remain hidden.",
      "numberInSurah": 18,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5342,
      "text": "Now as for him whose record shall be placed in his right hand, he will exclaim: \"Come you all!\" Read this my record!",
      "numberInSurah": 19,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5343,
      "text": "Behold, I did know that [one day] I would have to face my account!",
      "numberInSurah": 20,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5344,
      "text": "And so he will find himself in a happy state of life,",
      "numberInSurah": 21,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5345,
      "text": "in a lofty paradise,",
      "numberInSurah": 22,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5346,
      "text": "with its fruits within easy reach.",
      "numberInSurah": 23,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5347,
      "text": "[And all who are thus blest will be told:] \"Eat and drink with good cheer in return for all [the good deeds] that you have sent ahead in days gone by!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 24,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5348,
      "text": "But as for him whose record shall be placed in his left hand, he will exclaim: \"Oh, would that I had never been shown this my record,",
      "numberInSurah": 25,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5349,
      "text": "and neither known this my account!",
      "numberInSurah": 26,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5350,
      "text": "Oh, would that this [death of mine] had been the end of me!",
      "numberInSurah": 27,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5351,
      "text": "Of no avail to me is all that I have [ever] possessed,",
      "numberInSurah": 28,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5352,
      "text": "[and] all my power of argument has died away from me!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 29,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5353,
      "text": "Thereupon the command will go forth:] \"Lay hold of him, and shackle him,",
      "numberInSurah": 30,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5354,
      "text": "and then let him enter hell,",
      "numberInSurah": 31,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5355,
      "text": "and then thrust him into a chain [of other sinners like him - a chain] the length whereof is seventy cubits:",
      "numberInSurah": 32,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5356,
      "text": "for, behold, he did not believe in God, the Tremendous,",
      "numberInSurah": 33,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5357,
      "text": "and did not feel any urge to feed the needy:",
      "numberInSurah": 34,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 567,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5358,
      "text": "and so, no friend has here today,",
      "numberInSurah": 35,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5359,
      "text": "nor any food save the filth",
      "numberInSurah": 36,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5360,
      "text": "which none but the sinners eat!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 37,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 500,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5361,
      "text": "BUT NAY! I call to witness an that you can see,",
      "numberInSurah": 38,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5362,
      "text": "as well as all that you cannot see!",
      "numberInSurah": 39,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5363,
      "text": "Behold, this [Qur’an] is indeed the [inspired] word of a noble apostle,",
      "numberInSurah": 40,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5364,
      "text": "and is not – however little you may [be prepared to] believe it - the word of a poet;",
      "numberInSurah": 41,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5365,
      "text": "and neither is it - however little you may [be prepared to] take it to heart - the word of a soothsayer:",
      "numberInSurah": 42,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5366,
      "text": "[it is] a revelation from the Sustainer of all the worlds.",
      "numberInSurah": 43,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5367,
      "text": "Now if he [whom We have entrusted with it] had dared to attribute some [of his own] sayings unto Us,",
      "numberInSurah": 44,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5368,
      "text": "We would indeed have seized him by his right hand,",
      "numberInSurah": 45,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5369,
      "text": "and would indeed have cut his life-vein.",
      "numberInSurah": 46,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5370,
      "text": "and none of you could have saved him!",
      "numberInSurah": 47,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5371,
      "text": "And, verily, this [Qur’an] is a reminder to all the God-conscious!",
      "numberInSurah": 48,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5372,
      "text": "And, behold, well do We know that among you are such as will give the lie to it:",
      "numberInSurah": 49,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5373,
      "text": "yet, behold, this [rejection] will indeed become a source of bitter regret for all who deny the truth [of God's revelation] –",
      "numberInSurah": 50,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5374,
      "text": "for, verily, it is truth absolute!",
      "numberInSurah": 51,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5375,
      "text": "Extol, then the limitless glory of thy Sustainer's mighty name!",
      "numberInSurah": 52,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 501,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ],
  "source": "alquran.cloud",
  "scrapedAt": "2026-01-03T07:05:30.727Z"
}